display_name: SourcingProjectHistory transformation - 1000 - RAW test data sets_31 - Ariba Sourcing - 2

property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    'SourcingRequest_' || "SourcingProject"."ParentDocument_InternalId" as "SourcingRequest",
    'SourcingProject_' || "SourcingProject"."DocumentId_InternalId" as "SourcingProject",
    'SourcingProjectHistory_' || "SourcingProject"."InternalId" as "ID",
    "SourcingProject"."DocumentId_InternalId" as "DocumentIdInternalId",
    --"SourcingProject"."Owner" as "Owner",                                              JSON FORMAT
    --"SourcingProject"."DocumentId" as "DocumentId",                                              JSON FORMAT
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"SourcingProject"."CreateDate") as "CreateDate",
    "SourcingProject"."LastModified" as "LastModified",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,cast("SourcingProject"."TimeCreated" as timestamp)) as "TimeCreated",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"SourcingProject"."ContractEffectiveDate") as "ContractEffectiveDate",
    --"SourcingProject"."ProjectAddin" as "ProjectAddin",                                              JSON FORMAT
    "SourcingProject"."Status" as "Status",
    "SourcingProject"."UniqueId" as "UniqueId",
    "SourcingProject"."Active" as "Active",
    "SourcingProject"."NextVersion" as "ExtVersion",
    "SourcingProject"."Description" as "Description",
    "SourcingProject"."ProcessStatus" as "ProcessStatus",
    "SourcingProject"."Changed" as "Changed",
    "SourcingProject"."DocumentVersion" as "DocumentVersion",
    "SourcingProject"."IsVersionPinned" as "IsVersionPinned",
    "SourcingProject"."Title" as "TitleDefaultStringTranslation",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"SourcingProject"."TimeUpdated") as "TimeUpdated",
    "SourcingProject"."BaselineSpend" as "BaselineSpend",
    "SourcingProject"."ParentWorkspace" as "ParentWorkspace",
    "SourcingProject"."Alert" as "Alert",
    "SourcingProject"."ProcessId" as "ProcessId",
    "SourcingProject"."Owner_UniqueName" as "OwnerUniqueName",
    "SourcingProject"."ProjectAddin_IsTest" as "ProjectAddinIsTest",
    "SourcingProject"."ProjectAddin_FollowOnPath" as "ProjectAddinFollowOnPath",
    "SourcingProject"."ProjectAddin_Plan_Title_DefaultStringTranslation" as "ProjectAddinPlanTitleDefaultStringTranslation",
    "SourcingProject"."ProjectAddin_Plan_ProcessId" as "ProjectAddinPlanProcessId",
    "SourcingProject"."ProjectAddin_Plan_Workspace_InternalId" as "ProjectAddinPlanWorkspaceInternalId",
    "SourcingProject"."ProjectAddin_IsSubproject" as "ProjectAddinIsSubproject",
    "SourcingProject"."ParentDocument_InternalId" as "ParentDocumentInternalId",
    "SourcingProject"."Currency_UniqueName" as "CurrencyUniqueName",
    "SourcingProject"."TemplateObject_InternalId" as "TemplateObjectInternalId",
    "SourcingProject"."Description_DefaultStringTranslation" as "DescriptionDefaultStringTranslation",
    cast("SourcingProject"."BaselineSpend_Amount" as float) as "BaselineSpendAmount",
    "SourcingProject"."BaselineSpend_Currency_UniqueName" as "BaselineSpendCurrencyUniqueName",
    "SourcingProject"."ParentWorkspace_InternalId" as "ParentWorkspaceInternalId",
    "SourcingProject"."BaseLanguage_UniqueName" as "BaseLanguageUniqueName",
    "SourcingProject"."Owner_Name" as "OwnerName"
FROM "SourcingProject"
